WEBVTT

00:00:35.890 --> 00:00:38.430
=Angels and Guards=

00:00:38.430 --> 00:00:41.310
=Episode 16=

00:00:45.791 --> 00:00:46.416
Xu.

00:00:46.625 --> 00:00:48.541
When choosing a husband,
choose one who treats you well.

00:00:48.750 --> 00:00:50.166
After all, it is for life.

00:00:50.250 --> 00:00:51.083
I know.

00:00:51.875 --> 00:00:52.541
Constable Guan.

00:00:53.750 --> 00:00:55.208
Why are you drinking alone?

00:00:59.750 --> 00:01:00.291
Don't ask.

00:01:00.750 --> 00:01:01.958
Bingfan was promoted to Baihu today.

00:01:02.125 --> 00:01:03.375
I wanted to celebrate with her.

00:01:04.041 --> 00:01:05.375
But she took me to the bridge

00:01:05.375 --> 00:01:06.791
and said all kinds of strange things.

00:01:09.041 --> 00:01:09.541
Xu.

00:01:10.250 --> 00:01:11.000
You are close to her.

00:01:11.750 --> 00:01:12.541
Do you know

00:01:13.250 --> 00:01:15.708
if there is someone in Bingfan's heart?

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:18.000
As far as I know,

00:01:18.291 --> 00:01:19.541
Miss Shen cares
only about catching criminals.

00:01:20.125 --> 00:01:21.916
She does not care much for romance.

00:01:24.416 --> 00:01:25.041
I knew it.

00:01:26.416 --> 00:01:27.875
Then why did she say

00:01:28.958 --> 00:01:29.750
all those things to me today?

00:01:33.541 --> 00:01:34.375
I heard from Hua

00:01:34.750 --> 00:01:37.083
that Miss Shen carries a blood feud.

00:01:37.458 --> 00:01:38.750
She is determined to catch Leng Xin.

00:01:39.083 --> 00:01:40.458
And she swore

00:01:40.708 --> 00:01:42.916
that until Leng Xin is caught,

00:01:43.166 --> 00:01:44.958
she will not consider marriage.

00:01:45.541 --> 00:01:48.041
I think she said those harsh things
on purpose

00:01:48.250 --> 00:01:49.375
to make you give up

00:01:49.666 --> 00:01:50.416
so she wouldn't hold you back.

00:01:58.916 --> 00:01:59.916
That makes sense.

00:02:01.375 --> 00:02:01.833
Xu.

00:02:02.125 --> 00:02:03.583
You educated men really are sharp.

00:02:05.333 --> 00:02:06.541
Why did I not think of that?

00:02:07.916 --> 00:02:08.500
Then that means

00:02:09.500 --> 00:02:10.708
Bingfan does care about me.

00:02:12.833 --> 00:02:13.291
Constable Guan.

00:02:14.250 --> 00:02:14.958
In my opinion,

00:02:15.250 --> 00:02:16.958
a woman's heart is hard to read.

00:02:17.291 --> 00:02:18.625
If you truly like Miss Shen,

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:20.291
you must not give up halfway.

00:02:21.208 --> 00:02:23.333
Miss Shen is not heartless.

00:02:23.583 --> 00:02:25.375
As long as you stay sincere,

00:02:25.541 --> 00:02:27.708
she will come around with time.

00:02:28.250 --> 00:02:29.041
You are right.

00:02:29.333 --> 00:02:29.958
When pursuing a girl,

00:02:30.833 --> 00:02:31.333
I can’t back down.

00:02:31.958 --> 00:02:32.708
I took your advice.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:34.500
Now that I have cleared things up
with Guan Yunfeng,

00:02:35.833 --> 00:02:37.166
I feel much better.

00:02:38.500 --> 00:02:41.083
Then are you going to ask
Chang Beiming out tomorrow

00:02:41.500 --> 00:02:43.291
and do the same thing,

00:02:43.500 --> 00:02:44.750
making everything clear?

00:02:46.500 --> 00:02:47.375
Do you think I should?

00:02:50.916 --> 00:02:52.166
You two...

00:02:52.875 --> 00:02:54.416
I don't know.

00:02:55.041 --> 00:02:55.708
Why?

00:02:57.750 --> 00:02:59.166
No reason.

00:02:59.708 --> 00:03:03.166
It is hard to explain
and easy to get wrong.

00:03:26.520 --> 00:03:31.180
♪The past, like a song,
still echoes in my ears♪

00:03:31.890 --> 00:03:35.680
♪A scene of birds and dusk♪

00:03:37.060 --> 00:03:41.640
♪In the deep courtyard,
our eyes once met♪

00:03:41.850 --> 00:03:46.430
♪Like someone from a dream♪

00:03:49.208 --> 00:03:51.166
Come with me somewhere.

00:03:52.583 --> 00:03:53.250
All right.

00:03:57.390 --> 00:04:02.680
♪Yesterday is gone,
I only wait for you to return♪

00:04:02.930 --> 00:04:08.470
♪May we share one heart
until our hair turns white♪

00:04:14.208 --> 00:04:15.208
What you are wearing today

00:04:15.916 --> 00:04:16.958
is elegant and beautiful.

00:04:19.041 --> 00:04:21.416
I didn't understand
what a date meant before.

00:04:21.833 --> 00:04:23.833
That is why I made such a mess of it
last time.

00:04:24.833 --> 00:04:27.291
So this time, I chose something proper.

00:04:28.166 --> 00:04:29.166
Hua said a date

00:04:29.708 --> 00:04:32.541
is an important social engagement.

00:04:33.583 --> 00:04:34.208
You mean,

00:04:34.625 --> 00:04:36.000
today is a date?

00:04:44.375 --> 00:04:45.916
There are not many lakes or rivers
in the capital.

00:04:46.250 --> 00:04:47.708
One day, I will take you

00:04:48.666 --> 00:04:49.875
south to see the rivers

00:04:50.125 --> 00:04:50.625
and travel for a while.

00:04:51.875 --> 00:04:53.750
I have roamed the martial world
since childhood,

00:04:53.916 --> 00:04:54.916
wandering north and south.

00:04:55.541 --> 00:04:56.375
But this is my first time

00:04:56.500 --> 00:04:59.541
sitting quietly on a boat,

00:04:59.875 --> 00:05:00.625
taking in the view.

00:05:00.958 --> 00:05:01.666
Then

00:05:01.875 --> 00:05:04.208
enjoy this beautiful day.

00:05:12.333 --> 00:05:13.083
Beautiful, isn't it?

00:05:15.000 --> 00:05:15.791
Young Master Chang.

00:05:16.750 --> 00:05:18.375
You have enjoyed every worldly pleasure.

00:05:19.041 --> 00:05:20.333
Do you have any regrets?

00:05:23.250 --> 00:05:25.041
My one regret

00:05:25.958 --> 00:05:27.208
is that I have no one

00:05:27.458 --> 00:05:31.375
to hold hands with and roam the world
by boat.

00:05:32.666 --> 00:05:33.791
How do you men

00:05:33.916 --> 00:05:35.416
say things like that so easily?

00:05:36.458 --> 00:05:37.500
Every word is true.

00:05:38.666 --> 00:05:39.083
I don't believe that.

00:05:46.041 --> 00:05:46.875
Well,

00:05:47.208 --> 00:05:49.750
what do you think of
the phantom thief Feng Fuliu?

00:05:53.958 --> 00:05:54.750
Whether one is called

00:05:55.541 --> 00:05:57.333
a phantom thief, a gentleman thief,

00:05:57.958 --> 00:05:58.583
a wicked thief,

00:05:59.125 --> 00:05:59.666
or an evil thief

00:06:02.250 --> 00:06:04.041
often depends on a single thought.

00:06:05.791 --> 00:06:06.916
When it comes to good and evil,

00:06:08.625 --> 00:06:09.541
you can't judge by appearances alone.

00:06:13.000 --> 00:06:15.208
Whether Feng Fuliu is good or bad,

00:06:17.833 --> 00:06:20.000
you have to look closer to know.

00:06:22.291 --> 00:06:23.083
Enjoy the view.

00:06:35.375 --> 00:06:35.833
Come here.

00:06:48.458 --> 00:06:49.833
Why are there so many lanterns?

00:06:50.083 --> 00:06:52.291
People write their wishes on them

00:06:52.291 --> 00:06:54.416
and let them float downstream,
hoping they come true.

00:06:54.833 --> 00:06:55.833
Come true?

00:06:57.041 --> 00:06:57.541
Here.

00:07:00.416 --> 00:07:00.958
Thank you.

00:07:07.720 --> 00:07:10.430
(May my father, Shen Lian,
be cleared of all false charges soon.)

00:07:12.333 --> 00:07:14.250
Good.

00:07:30.708 --> 00:07:33.458
Don't tell me you wished
to catch Feng Fuliu.

00:07:34.791 --> 00:07:35.916
I can't tell you that.

00:07:36.083 --> 00:07:37.000
You don't have to. I know.

00:07:40.541 --> 00:07:41.250
Young Master Chang.

00:07:41.666 --> 00:07:42.000
Actually...

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:42.750
Don't say it.

00:07:43.875 --> 00:07:44.666
I know everything.

00:07:45.583 --> 00:07:46.791
You know what I am going to say?

00:07:48.541 --> 00:07:49.541
Those words of yours

00:07:50.041 --> 00:07:51.458
may fool Guan Yunfeng,

00:07:52.500 --> 00:07:53.041
but Bingfan,

00:07:54.375 --> 00:07:54.875
I understand you.

00:07:55.750 --> 00:07:56.875
I know your heart,

00:07:57.083 --> 00:07:58.291
and you should know mine.

00:07:59.125 --> 00:08:00.625
You are not someone who gives up easily.

00:08:01.416 --> 00:08:02.791
And I am not someone
who changes his heart.

00:08:04.416 --> 00:08:05.166
So today,

00:08:06.583 --> 00:08:07.375
let us not talk about that.

00:08:08.083 --> 00:08:09.041
Let us just enjoy the night.

00:08:12.041 --> 00:08:13.333
Hua was right.

00:08:14.041 --> 00:08:16.000
Talking to you only makes things
harder to explain.

00:08:16.583 --> 00:08:17.000
Look.

00:08:17.708 --> 00:08:18.708
Beautiful fireworks.

00:09:05.875 --> 00:09:07.250
(Why was it so easy)

00:09:07.583 --> 00:09:09.625
(to make everything clear
with Guan Yunfeng?)

00:09:11.208 --> 00:09:12.416
(But with Chang Beiming,)

00:09:13.583 --> 00:09:14.375
(I can't)

00:09:15.291 --> 00:09:16.375
(even say the words.)

00:09:25.250 --> 00:09:26.375
Xintian, look.

00:09:26.500 --> 00:09:28.083
Duoyu is really good with his hands.

00:09:28.250 --> 00:09:29.291
He altered it to fit perfectly.

00:09:29.666 --> 00:09:30.666
It does fit well.

00:09:31.791 --> 00:09:33.791
But one of you has Duoyu,

00:09:34.208 --> 00:09:35.375
and the other has Young Master Chang.

00:09:36.041 --> 00:09:37.208
That leaves me all alone,

00:09:37.833 --> 00:09:38.833
poor and lonely.

00:09:39.375 --> 00:09:39.833
I'm leaving.

00:09:40.166 --> 00:09:42.041
Which of the two is your type?

00:09:42.541 --> 00:09:45.125
Duoyu is thoughtful,
but not manly enough.

00:09:45.333 --> 00:09:47.875
Young Master Chang is handsome,

00:09:48.250 --> 00:09:49.958
but I always find him a little scary.

00:09:50.416 --> 00:09:51.916
The day before we tried
to catch Feng Fuliu,

00:09:52.291 --> 00:09:53.791
Young Master Chang came to me

00:09:53.791 --> 00:09:55.083
and asked about our plan.

00:09:56.041 --> 00:09:57.791
I didn't think much of it then.

00:09:58.416 --> 00:10:00.083
Now it finally hit me.

00:10:00.458 --> 00:10:02.208
No wonder he was not at the meeting.

00:10:02.916 --> 00:10:04.750
He was tricking it out of me.

00:10:05.416 --> 00:10:06.458
You mean

00:10:08.250 --> 00:10:10.000
the night before the princess's case,

00:10:11.083 --> 00:10:12.666
Young Master Chang came
to pump you for information?

00:10:22.333 --> 00:10:23.125
You want to talk to me?

00:10:26.000 --> 00:10:26.791
Young Master Chang.

00:10:28.750 --> 00:10:30.958
Are you really the phantom thief
Feng Fuliu?

00:10:32.125 --> 00:10:32.916
Hua.

00:10:33.458 --> 00:10:34.458
Why?

00:10:36.750 --> 00:10:38.250
I just want to know the truth.

00:10:38.250 --> 00:10:39.458
I mean no bad.

00:10:40.375 --> 00:10:41.083
Truth?

00:10:41.958 --> 00:10:45.166
The Ever-Changing Wildcat
Hua Yunfeng's signature move

00:10:45.666 --> 00:10:46.625
is the Three Wildcat Leaps.

00:10:48.250 --> 00:10:51.500
So are you the Ever-Changing Wildcat,
Hua Yunfeng?

00:11:08.125 --> 00:11:10.750
The spring wind dares
to brush the willows.

00:11:13.416 --> 00:11:14.583
The night rain comes unseen

00:11:16.166 --> 00:11:17.208
to nourish the flowers.

00:11:33.125 --> 00:11:34.250
Let's drink up today.

00:11:37.625 --> 00:11:38.708
Watch where you are going!

00:11:39.125 --> 00:11:39.375
I...

00:11:39.625 --> 00:11:40.500
Forgive me, sir.

00:11:41.375 --> 00:11:42.208
Xu Duoyu,

00:11:42.833 --> 00:11:43.583
how come

00:11:43.583 --> 00:11:44.958
we haven't seen

00:11:44.958 --> 00:11:45.875
Miss Hua come to see you lately?

00:11:45.958 --> 00:11:46.916
Squad Leader Hua is on a mission.

00:11:47.125 --> 00:11:47.750
Nonsense.

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:49.416
What darn mission could
a female Jinyiwei have?

00:11:50.041 --> 00:11:50.666
Exactly.

00:11:52.666 --> 00:11:54.958
She got tired of you
and kicked you aside, didn't she?

00:11:55.541 --> 00:11:56.125
Hey,

00:11:56.416 --> 00:11:58.916
if she is bored with you,
why not pass her to me?

00:12:04.666 --> 00:12:05.500
Don't insult Hua.

00:12:07.250 --> 00:12:08.583
Who do you think you are talking to,
you punk?

00:12:09.708 --> 00:12:12.291
A lowly servant dares to talk back
to his superiors?

00:12:12.666 --> 00:12:13.916
And you are defending her?

00:12:14.458 --> 00:12:16.125
Hua Mange is nothing but a loose woman.

00:12:16.416 --> 00:12:17.166
She is just stringing you along.

00:12:17.333 --> 00:12:18.500
Take a look at yourself.

00:12:18.666 --> 00:12:19.666
Why would she

00:12:19.666 --> 00:12:21.458
ever be interested in you?

00:12:21.916 --> 00:12:22.958
Shut up!

00:12:31.208 --> 00:12:32.041
Duoyu!

00:12:33.000 --> 00:12:33.500
Hua.

00:12:33.875 --> 00:12:34.833
Duoyu.

00:12:36.458 --> 00:12:37.250
Does it hurt?

00:12:44.833 --> 00:12:46.458
Those people went too far.

00:12:46.958 --> 00:12:48.375
They should know whose dog
they are kicking.

00:12:48.583 --> 00:12:49.208
Hua.

00:12:49.708 --> 00:12:51.000
You think I'm a dog?

00:12:52.583 --> 00:12:54.416
I'm worried about you.

00:12:54.583 --> 00:12:55.875
Why did they hit you?

00:12:57.458 --> 00:13:00.083
They were saying awful things about you.
I couldn't stand it.

00:13:00.500 --> 00:13:01.541
So I fought them.

00:13:02.708 --> 00:13:03.708
They have a death wish.

00:13:10.333 --> 00:13:10.958
You bold thief!

00:13:11.125 --> 00:13:12.291
Trying to break into the Archives again?

00:13:13.458 --> 00:13:14.041
Get her!

00:13:14.500 --> 00:13:15.500
Hurry! Don't let her escape!

00:13:33.916 --> 00:13:35.000
What happened?

00:13:35.166 --> 00:13:36.375
Where did their hair go?

00:13:40.250 --> 00:13:40.791
Get away.

00:13:41.625 --> 00:13:42.541
So shiny.

00:13:42.541 --> 00:13:43.416
What are you staring at?

00:13:43.416 --> 00:13:44.250
Won't even let us touch it?

00:13:49.291 --> 00:13:50.541
Mr. Lu.

00:13:53.583 --> 00:13:54.333
What happened?

00:13:54.708 --> 00:13:56.125
I... I don't know.

00:13:56.333 --> 00:13:58.500
It was fine before I went to sleep
last night.

00:13:58.500 --> 00:14:00.166
Then I woke up, and my hair was gone.

00:14:02.958 --> 00:14:03.500
Useless fools!

00:14:04.875 --> 00:14:05.791
You went to sleep with hair

00:14:06.500 --> 00:14:07.583
and woke up bald?

00:14:08.916 --> 00:14:09.708
If that thief

00:14:10.208 --> 00:14:11.250
had wanted your heads

00:14:11.250 --> 00:14:12.208
instead of your hair,

00:14:12.416 --> 00:14:13.833
you would all be dead by now.

00:14:14.458 --> 00:14:15.291
Sorry.

00:14:15.333 --> 00:14:16.250
Sorry.

00:14:16.958 --> 00:14:18.791
My lord, I checked the room.

00:14:19.291 --> 00:14:20.416
The doors and windows are all intact.

00:14:21.000 --> 00:14:21.958
It must have been done by an expert.

00:14:23.375 --> 00:14:23.833
My lord.

00:14:24.416 --> 00:14:25.958
In the martial world, only two people

00:14:26.375 --> 00:14:27.125
have such footwork.

00:14:27.666 --> 00:14:28.791
One is the phantom thief Feng Fuliu.

00:14:29.000 --> 00:14:29.541
The other is

00:14:29.791 --> 00:14:31.291
the Ever-Changing Wildcat, Hua Yunfeng.

00:14:39.560 --> 00:14:42.310
(Northern Bureau)

00:14:43.500 --> 00:14:44.166
Duoyu.

00:14:44.875 --> 00:14:45.958
Tell me the truth.

00:14:46.416 --> 00:14:47.375
Who exactly are you?

00:14:49.458 --> 00:14:50.000
Hua.

00:14:50.833 --> 00:14:51.833
What do you mean?

00:14:52.208 --> 00:14:53.833
You don't seem like

00:14:54.833 --> 00:14:57.708
an ordinary servant to me.

00:14:57.916 --> 00:14:59.750
I am just an ordinary servant.

00:15:00.250 --> 00:15:02.166
Fine. You won't tell me the truth?

00:15:03.000 --> 00:15:04.708
Then don't speak to me again.

00:15:05.083 --> 00:15:05.625
Hua.

00:15:06.291 --> 00:15:08.041
Please let me keep a few secrets.

00:15:10.708 --> 00:15:11.541
All right, all right.

00:15:12.375 --> 00:15:14.916
I was teasing you.
Look how nervous you got.

00:15:19.458 --> 00:15:20.708
You spend every day studying

00:15:20.708 --> 00:15:22.458
these strange little things.

00:15:22.458 --> 00:15:23.291
Do you never get tired of it?

00:15:23.666 --> 00:15:24.125
Hua.

00:15:24.625 --> 00:15:25.625
Don't underestimate them.

00:15:26.166 --> 00:15:27.458
They can be very powerful.

00:15:28.041 --> 00:15:28.833
When you are catching criminals,

00:15:29.291 --> 00:15:31.333
they might help in ways
you never expect.

00:15:32.250 --> 00:15:32.791
Really?

00:15:34.500 --> 00:15:36.333
I still trust martial arts more.

00:15:51.625 --> 00:15:52.875
Good thing it was a dud.

00:16:11.041 --> 00:16:13.500
How long do you plan to stay
on top of me?

00:16:18.958 --> 00:16:19.583
Sorry.

00:16:20.291 --> 00:16:21.291
I didn't mean to.

00:16:26.458 --> 00:16:27.208
Duoyu.

00:16:29.000 --> 00:16:30.208
You are getting cheeky too.

00:16:33.350 --> 00:16:34.560
(Yanyu Tower)

00:16:37.125 --> 00:16:37.875
Embroidered Spring Blade?

00:16:38.583 --> 00:16:39.500
You are a Jinyiwei?

00:16:42.625 --> 00:16:43.500
A female one?

00:16:44.416 --> 00:16:45.708
Don't kill me!

00:16:46.250 --> 00:16:47.041
Don't kill me!

00:16:52.791 --> 00:16:53.500
Commissioner.

00:16:56.625 --> 00:16:59.125
We arrested Hu Ke, Director
at the Ministry of War, under orders.

00:16:59.458 --> 00:17:00.083
We are here to report.

00:17:01.416 --> 00:17:01.833
Good.

00:17:02.458 --> 00:17:03.125
Very good.

00:17:11.916 --> 00:17:13.333
Why are the files on Leng Xin

00:17:13.500 --> 00:17:14.833
and the files
on Prince Luo's treason case

00:17:14.833 --> 00:17:15.625
all missing?

00:17:17.416 --> 00:17:18.958
Those classified files

00:17:19.500 --> 00:17:20.458
were all transferred out

00:17:21.083 --> 00:17:22.458
three days ago.

00:17:22.916 --> 00:17:23.791
Who transferred them?

00:17:24.458 --> 00:17:25.083
Well...

00:17:26.041 --> 00:17:27.416
Did you collude with someone

00:17:27.708 --> 00:17:28.833
to destroy those secret files?

00:17:29.500 --> 00:17:30.875
I would never dare.

00:17:31.291 --> 00:17:33.500
But the person who transferred them...

00:17:33.833 --> 00:17:34.250
Who?

00:17:35.041 --> 00:17:36.125
It was the Commander.

00:17:42.416 --> 00:17:44.000
Who upset you this time?

00:17:44.916 --> 00:17:45.500
My lord.

00:17:46.083 --> 00:17:48.208
You transferred the Northern Bureau's
secret files on Leng Xin,

00:17:48.375 --> 00:17:49.500
as well as the files
on Prince Luo's case.

00:17:49.875 --> 00:17:51.958
Don't I have the authority?

00:17:52.791 --> 00:17:53.708
Did you do it on purpose?

00:17:54.250 --> 00:17:55.291
Why would you say that?

00:17:55.291 --> 00:17:56.333
I was just promoted to Baihu

00:17:56.833 --> 00:17:57.958
and finally gained access to them.

00:17:58.291 --> 00:18:00.250
Then you transferred them
three days ago.

00:18:00.250 --> 00:18:01.500
Are you starting

00:18:02.708 --> 00:18:04.041
to suspect me again?

00:18:04.958 --> 00:18:06.125
If I suspected you,

00:18:06.666 --> 00:18:08.125
I wouldn't have come
to ask you directly.

00:18:12.166 --> 00:18:13.083
To tell you the truth,

00:18:13.875 --> 00:18:15.208
three days ago,

00:18:15.791 --> 00:18:17.291
I suddenly received
a secret imperial order.

00:18:17.625 --> 00:18:19.250
His Majesty wanted to review

00:18:19.625 --> 00:18:21.708
all files related
to Prince Luo's case himself.

00:18:38.520 --> 00:18:41.690
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

00:18:42.060 --> 00:18:45.440
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

00:18:45.690 --> 00:18:48.690
♪My heart drifted lost♪

00:18:48.690 --> 00:18:52.100
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

00:18:53.190 --> 00:18:56.400
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

00:18:56.810 --> 00:19:00.150
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

00:19:00.730 --> 00:19:02.940
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

00:19:02.940 --> 00:19:06.980
♪I've softly let it go♪

00:19:06.980 --> 00:19:10.850
♪The vow you made was true♪

00:19:10.850 --> 00:19:14.600
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

00:19:14.900 --> 00:19:16.810
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

00:19:16.810 --> 00:19:21.350
♪And forget at world's end♪

00:19:21.650 --> 00:19:23.150
♪Embracing memory♪

00:19:23.150 --> 00:19:25.520
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

00:19:25.520 --> 00:19:29.400
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

00:19:29.400 --> 00:19:31.730
♪I wish to let it pass♪

00:19:31.730 --> 00:19:36.730
♪And run toward this vast life♪